	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Let me see if i got it right.<br />UNROM to UOROM on Konami board<br />Bend up eprom pins 1, 2, 24, 30, 31, and 32.<br />Bend up MC74HC32 pin 3.<br />Solder pin 1 to hole 14.<br />Solder pin 2 to hole 22.<br />Solder pin 30 to MC74HC32 pin 3.<br />Solder pin 32 to hole 28.<br />Edit...<br />Works as far as i can tell. Thanks.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


